window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Your mind is his playground. </b></p> <p>A gruesome triple homicide. There’s only one surviving witness - the boy whose family was killed before his eyes...and he can’t remember what happened.&nbsp;</p> <p>The police are desperate for information. Detective Joona Linna enlists the help of hypnotist Erik Maria Bark. But when Bark unlocks the secrets in the boy’s memory, he triggers a terrifying chain of events that will put all their lives in jeopardy.&nbsp;</p>"; 
